\"><span class=\"font-scale-7\">Troy Hunt, Microsoft Regional Director &amp; MVP</span></span></span></p><p class=\"line-height-scale-5 font-scale-4 text-align-left\">Troy is a world renouned security expert. Troy travels the world educating people on security vunerabilites and how to mitigate those risks.</p><p class=\"line-height-scale-5 font-scale-4 text-align-left\">Troy has serveral amazing videos on <a href=\"http://app.pluralsight.com/author/troy-hunt\" target=\"_blank\">Pluralsight </a>with a focus once again on security vunerabilites.</p><p class=\"line-height-scale-5 font-scale-4 text-align-left\">He is also the founder and creator of <a href=\"https://haveibeenpwned.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Have I been Pwned, </a>a free service that aggregates data breaches and helps people establish if they\'ve been impacted by malicious activity on the web. As well as being a useful service for the community.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"\" class=\"layout flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-column\"><div style=\"\" class=\"row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"composite flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-composite flex flex--12 undefined\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12 widget-widget\"><div class=\"widget\" data-widget-id=\"fc9e6d9b-7148-1dfb-8241-382e3c719bf9\"><div class=\"lp-headline\" spellcheck=\"false\"><h1 class=\"line-height-scale-3 font-scale-5 text-align-center lp-headline headline\"><strong>What Will The Workshop Cover</strong></h1></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"\" class=\"layout flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"column flex__item--md-6 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-column\"><div style=\"\" class=\"row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"composite flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-composite flex flex--12 undefined\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12 widget-widget\"><div class=\"widget\" data-widget-id=\"c44cf4b7-1444-761c-d7d3-0dbf266fb534\"><div class=\"lp-headline\" spellcheck=\"false\"><h1 class=\"line-height-scale-3 font-scale-5 text-align-center lp-headline headline\">Cross Site Scripting</h1></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"\" class=\"row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"composite flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-composite flex flex--12 undefined\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12 widget-widget\"><div class=\"widget\" data-widget-id=\"e0984f8e-5c88-0608-401c-e9f629b8e4c8\"><div class=\"lp-video has-content lp-video--small\" data-widget-type=\"lp-video\">  <div id=\"video-target\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LBj0kEmapoE\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\"></iframe></div> </div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"\" class=\"column flex__item--md-6 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-column\"><div style=\"\" class=\"row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"composite flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-composite flex flex--12 undefined\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12 widget-widget\"><div class=\"widget\" data-widget-id=\"843f60d6-20bb-9bbd-a9f9-61d723172f39\"><div class=\"lp-headline\" spellcheck=\"false\"><h1 class=\"line-height-scale-3 font-scale-5 text-align-center lp-headline headline\"><strong>SQL Injection</strong></h1></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"\" class=\"row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"composite flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-composite flex flex--12 undefined\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12 widget-widget\"><div class=\"widget\" data-widget-id=\"10f4ba9a-670a-8d2c-de8b-45f93661871e\"><div class=\"lp-video has-content lp-video--small\" data-widget-type=\"lp-video\">  <div id=\"video-target\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/O4YyihOZheo\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\"></iframe></div> </div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"\" class=\"layout flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-column\"><div style=\"\" class=\"row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"composite flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-composite flex flex--12 undefined\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12 widget-widget\"><div class=\"widget\" data-widget-id=\"0abed967-5b85-a199-283b-c1af126306e3\"><div class=\"lp-text\" style=\"min-height:20px;outline:0\" spellcheck=\"false\"><p class=\"line-height-scale-3 font-scale-4 text-align-left\"><strong>\"Hack Yourself First\" </strong>is all about building up defensive skills in software developers. It looks at security from the attacker\'s perspective and takes them through the steps necessary to exploit vulnerable software on the web so that they can experience hacking first hand. Workshop participants are set specific goals they must complete that involve probing for risks and then exploiting discrete vulnerabilities in a specially built vulnerable application. The interactive nature of the workshop means that multiple attack vectors are usually identified across the spectrum of participants and each person contributes their own unique perspective as to how specific risks are exploited.</p><p class=\"line-height-scale-3 font-scale-4 text-align-left\">The objective of the workshop is that each person walks away with demonstrated experience across a broad spectrum of specific risks. They not only learn about but also demonstrate practical experience across a range of different vulnerabilities targeted to the specific needs of the group.</p><p class=\"line-height-scale-3 font-scale-4 text-align-left\"><strong>Please visit Troy\'s webpage for a full list of details <a href=\"https://www.troyhunt.com/workshops/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.troyhunt.com/workshops/</a></strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section style=\"background-color: rgb(114, 123, 132); border-color: rgb(114, 123, 132);\" class=\"section\"><div class=\"container\"></div></section><section style=\"\" class=\"section\"><div class=\"container\"><div style=\"\" class=\"layout flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-column\"><div style=\"\" class=\"row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"composite flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-composite flex flex--12 undefined\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12 widget-widget\"><div class=\"widget\" data-widget-id=\"f5420775-9163-70ee-9614-7627173497af\"><div class=\"lp-headline\" spellcheck=\"false\"><h1 class=\"line-height-scale-3 font-scale-6 text-align-center lp-headline headline\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto;\"><strong>How do we get Troy to come to Minneapolis</strong></span></h1></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"\" class=\"row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"composite flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-composite flex flex--12 undefined\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12 widget-widget\"><div class=\"widget\" data-widget-id=\"22d35d63-42aa-accb-4151-9e4d6c152899\"><div class=\"lp-text\" style=\"min-height:20px;outline:0\" spellcheck=\"false\"><p class=\"line-height-scale-3 font-scale-4 text-align-left\">Troy teaches all around the world, and we are lucky enough that he is already going to be here in Minneapolis in July. However as with everything in life all good things are not free. Troy\'s single day workshops are not cheap and require paying travel costs. As stated before we are lucky enough to already have in him in Minneapolis in July so those travel costs should be relatively in expensive.</p><p class=\"line-height-scale-3 font-scale-4 text-align-left\">We would like to keep the class size as small as possible roughly 15-20 people but we could go higher if needed to lower individual costs.</p><p class=\"line-height-scale-3 font-scale-4 text-align-left\">Right now I am looking for a list of people who would be interested so we can make this affordable to everyone who wants to come. I would imagine minus any sort of corporate sponsorship we could get to send their employees to the traning we would divide the cost of everyone who wants to attend.</p><p class=\"line-height-scale-3 font-scale-4 text-align-left\">If you are at all interested, please send me an email by filling out the form below and I will try to get a head count and keep everyone up to date with how many people we have looking to come.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"\" class=\"row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"composite flex__item--md-6 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-composite flex flex--12 undefined\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12 widget-widget\"><div class=\"widget\" data-widget-id=\"b7023095-e4dd-1812-27a1-f49666bbe055\"><style>[data-widget-id=\"b7023095-e4dd-1812-27a1-f49666bbe055\"] .lp-button--flat,[data-widget-id=\"b7023095-e4dd-1812-27a1-f49666bbe055\"] .lp-button--flat:active,[data-widget-id=\"b7023095-e4dd-1812-27a1-f49666bbe055\"] .lp-button--flat:focus{border-color:rgb(236, 109, 32);background:rgb(236, 109, 32);color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)}[data-widget-id=\"b7023095-e4dd-1812-27a1-f49666bbe055\"] .lp-button--flat:hover{border-color:rgb(185, 85, 25);background:rgb(185, 85, 25);color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)}</style><div class=\"btn-container\"> <!--<view>--><a href=\"1432b3173f72a2:1146c7748346dc\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\" target=\"\" rel=\"\" class=\"lp-button--small is-bold lp-button--flat font-scale-7 line-height-scale-7 lp-button js-leadbox-trigger\">&nbsp; &nbsp; SIGN ME UP &nbsp; &nbsp;</a><!--</view>--><!--anchor--> <!--anchor--> <!--anchor--> </div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"\" class=\"composite flex__item--md-6 flex__item--xs-12\"><div class=\"inner-composite flex flex--12 undefined\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-column flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"widget-row flex flex--12\"><div style=\"\" class=\"flex__item--md-12 flex__item--xs-12 widget-widget\"><div class=\"widget\" data-widget-id=\"67f8e2e7-1dee-db78-a212-b1d24dbc906a\"><style>[data-widget-id=\"67f8e2e7-1dee-db78-a212-b1d24dbc906a\"] .lp-button--flat,[data-widget-id=\"67f8e2e7-1dee-db78-a212-b1d24dbc906a\"] .lp-button--flat:active,[data-widget-id=\"67f8e2e7-1dee-db78-a212-b1d24d